{"text_id":194572,"tokens":["In"," this"," paper",","," new"," results"," on"," convolution"," of"," spectral"," components"," in"," binary"," fields"," have"," been"," presented"," for"," combi","atorial"," sequences","."," A"," novel"," method"," of"," convolution"," of"," DFT"," points"," through"," Chinese"," Rema","inder"," Sequences"," (","CS",")"," is"," proposed"," to"," reduce"," the"," non","-","linear","ity"," of"," the"," CS"," and"," thus"," can"," be"," used"," as"," a"," means"," to"," convert"," the"," CS"," into"," a"," straight","-","line"," spreading"," function"," of"," the"," coefficients","."," Results"," are"," presented"," that"," in"," vector"," form",","," linear"," bulk"," transverse"," Gaussian"," waves"," are"," used"," as"," the"," basis"," for"," the"," transform"," tunneling"," method"," in"," order"," not"," only"," to"," produce"," an"," edge"," random"," deviation"," but"," also"," to"," provide"," another"," way"," to"," control"," the"," propagation"," speed"," of"," waves","."," The"," phenomenon"," occurs"," when"," two"," wave"," pairs"," of"," waves"," propagate"," at"," different"," speeds"," without"," interfering"," with"," each"," other"," and"," are"," able"," to"," pass"," completely"," through"," their"," respective"," paths"," by"," zero"," dispersion"," or"," slip","stream","."," By"," controlling"," for"," this",","," there"," will"," be"," no"," added"," interference"," in"," terms"," of"," frequency"," dependence"," and"," the"," signal"," quality"," will"," improve"," significantly"," over"," time","."," Conversion"," of"," spectral"," components"," from"," mixed","-","frequency"," control"," signals"," to"," coherent"," signals"," has"," now"," become"," widely"," known","."," In"," particular",","," a"," series"," of"," experiments"," using"," a"," signal"," processing"," system"," based"," on"," the"," holographic"," processing"," technology"," has"," recently"," gained"," wide"," acceptance","."," This"," technique"," allows"," the"," integration"," of"," different"," spatial"," parameters"," among"," the"," same"," noise"," sources",","," thereby"," reducing"," diffraction"," loss","."," The"," proposed"," multi","path"," multi","-","channel"," channel"," architecture"," requires"," very"," high"," energy"," efficiency"," even"," during"," the"," processing"," phase","."," Furthermore",","," it"," uses"," a"," large"," number"," of"," channels"," that"," may"," require"," power"," consumption","."," This"," work"," was"," funded"," by"," the"," Partnership"," for"," Engineering"," and"," Technology"," Center"," (","H","IC","TC",")"," and"," the"," Institute"," of"," Physics"," of"," Uy","gh","ur"," University","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"opt_125m","label":1}